::KitKat:
"We shall return to the base once we have Megatron's spark and given 
Hell Beast what remains of the body." She had heard quarreling from 
inside the cave. "Is everything alright Destrustor? I thought I heard 
an argument?" She then turned her attention to Bludgeon. "Take out 
the spark please and then hand it to me. Then if you would be kind 
enough to cut the body down for Hell Beast.  After that, we leave."
